A '''huun''' was a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] weapon designed by [[Mezhan Kwaad]]. A small nut, it released nerve gas strong enough to kill a large mass of people. She herself was immune to its poisons. After killing [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Tsaak Vootuh]], Kwaad threatened to kill a crowd of Vong with her huun.

